last_episode_to_air.overview: Ra-ra performs a dazzling duet with Jun by her side in spirit. Man-bok regains his health, and Eun-seok rediscovers love.

name: Do Do Sol Sol La La Sol
overview: A riches-to-rags pianist who loses everything but her smile is guided by twinkling little stars to a small town where she finds hope, home and love.

episodes.name: Do Do Sol Sol La La Sol
episodes.overview: It's Gu Ra-ra's big day. Sunwoo Jun catches her off-guard with a memorable first encounter, moments before her world comes crashing down.

episodes.name: Pianist Patient
episodes.overview: Jun finds himself unable to leave Ra-ra's side after she leans on him for support. Cha Eun-seok becomes curious about Jun and protective of Ra-ra.

episodes.name: Da Capo
episodes.overview: Ra-ra starts again from scratch with the help of old dreams and new neighbors. As Eun-seok gazes from afar, Jun looks out for Ra-ra day and night.

episodes.name: LaLa Piano Land
episodes.overview: With the help of generous supporters, La La Piano Land opens its doors. Jun and Eun-seok vie for a spot in Ra-ra's heart and on her piano bench.

episodes.name: Night and Dreams
episodes.overview: Jun slowly opens up to Ra-ra, who warmly embraces his sadness. Eun-seok is surprised to learn about Jun's true identity.

episodes.name: Secrets and Lies
episodes.overview: The traumatic incident behind Jun's secretive life is revealed. A mischievous salon customer joins La La Piano Land as an overzealous student.

episodes.name: You Are So Special
episodes.overview: Jun’s mom gets closer to his whereabouts. After anonymously holding Ra-ra’s hand through dark times, Eun-seok makes a move in real life.

episodes.name: Pleasure of Love
episodes.overview: Ra-ra and Jun get honest about their feelings. La La Piano Land piques the interest of more out-of-town visitors.

episodes.name: The Night of Thunder
episodes.overview: The townspeople become increasingly wary of An Jung-ho. On the day of the piano competition, he wreaks havoc on Ra-ra's life.

episodes.name: Who Are You?
episodes.overview: The kidnapping ends with one man in handcuffs and two people on stretchers. Jun is faced with an inescapable reunion and farewell.

episodes.name: Reunion
episodes.overview: Jin Ha-yeong and Lee Seung-gi venture to Seoul to rescue Jun. Ra-ra holds a recital for Kim Man-bok to perform a song in loving memory of his wife.

episodes.name: Hochzeitsmarsch
episodes.overview: Cho Yun-sil asks Ra-ra for her cooperation as Jun works hard to get his academic life back on track. A new couple walks down the aisle.

episodes.name: Romance Without Words
episodes.overview: Jun's blunder helps promote Ha-yeong and Seung-gi's small business. Ra-ra belatedly learns the identity of the piano donor.

episodes.name: A Furtive Tear
episodes.overview: Reconnecting with a friend from the past, Jun makes sudden changes to the present. Seung-gi fulfills his childhood wish.

episodes.name: Farewell
episodes.overview: Ra-ra finally remembers her first encounter with Jun. Jun tells a white lie before departing on a nerve-wracking journey.

episodes.name: Do Do Sol Sol La La Sol
episodes.overview: Ra-ra performs a dazzling duet with Jun by her side in spirit. Man-bok regains his health, and Eun-seok rediscovers love.
